---
title: Jamaican Roasted Eggplant with Spinach Rice & Coconut Sauce
description: When this dish was brought to our test kitchen table, it disappeared in record time! With a delicious
combination of spinach rice, tender eggplant, toasted almonds and a punchy Caribbean coconut sauce, it's
sure to be a hit at your table too.
